wiki.summary: The third track on So Much Fun, “Ecstasy,” is filled with drug references and experiences including, molly, weed, codeine, and percocets. Over a hard hitting beat produced by DY Krazy and 12 Hunna, Thug raps about embracing the druggy lifestyle of hip-hop by consistently getting high and partying. On September 2018, Thug was arrested on a number of drug possession-related charges after he was taken into custody for possession and intent to distribute meth, hydrocodone, and marijuana. Read more on Last.fm.
